OL,3,CMore ethnic minority graduates feel
OL,4,Cdisadvantaged in job applications
OL,6,FMore male and ethnic minority
OL,7,Fgraduates feel disadvantaged in job
OL,8,Fapplications, a survey has suggested.
OL,10,FThere has been a rise in graduates
OL,11,Freporting that their ethnic
OL,12,Fbackground, gender, social class or
OL,13,Fdisability is holding them back from
OL,14,Ffinding work, according to graduate
OL,15,Fcareers service Prospects.
