OL,3,CMore ethnic minority graduates feel
OL,4,Cdisadvantaged in job applications
OL,6,FProspects' annual Early Careers
OL,7,FSurvey, from education technology
OL,8,Forganisation Jisc, saw increases
OL,9,Facross the board in respondents
OL,10,Ffeeling disadvantaged in the job
OL,11,Fapplication process due to a personal
OL,12,Fcharacteristic.
OL,14,FThe survey found that 54% of ethnic
OL,15,Fminority graduates felt disadvantaged
OL,16,Fwhen applying for jobs because of
OL,17,Ftheir ethnicity, compared with 43%
OL,18,Flast year.
