OL,3,CMore ethnic minority graduates feel
OL,4,Cdisadvantaged in job applications
OL,6,FBut the proportion of males who
OL,7,Freported being held back due to their
OL,8,Fgender more than doubled from 4% last
OL,9,Fyear.
OL,11,FThere were also more reports of people
OL,12,Ffeeling disadvantaged because of their
OL,13,Fsexual orientation, social class or
OL,14,Fdisability than in the previous survey.
OL,16,FChris Rea, a careers expert at
OL,17,FProspects for Jisc, said it's
OL,18,F"concerning" that more graduates are
OL,19,Ffeeling the odds are against them.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G4/7
