OL,3,CMore ethnic minority graduates feel
OL,4,Cdisadvantaged in job applications
OL,6,F"We have also found young people,
OL,7,Fparticularly disadvantaged groups, are
OL,8,Fstruggling with motivation.
OL,10,F"The jobs market is particularly
OL,11,Fcompetitive and that could be having
OL,12,Fan impact on how they're feeling.
OL,13,FWhile graduates may feel disadvantaged
OL,14,Fthis doesn't mean they should be
OL,15,Fdemoralised."
OL,17,F"Most employers strive to be more
OL,18,Finclusive and see the benefit of
OL,19,Fdiverse teams and it's important that
OL,20,Fwe get this message through to young
OL,21,Fpeople."
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G5/7
