OL,3,CMore ethnic minority graduates feel
OL,4,Cdisadvantaged in job applications
OL,6,F"Employers can help by being
OL,7,Ftransparent about recruitment
OL,8,Fprocesses and any support they offer."
OL,10,FA total of 6,102 people were surveyed
OL,11,Fin January and February and the
OL,12,Fmajority of respondents were in
OL,13,Femployment or studying at university.
OL,15,FThe survey included some pupils in
OL,16,Fsecondary schools, sixth forms and
OL,17,Fcolleges, as well as apprentices and
OL,18,Fjobseekers.
